Usage
=====
important
---------
<esc> is unmaped in input mode, instead 'jk' comb. is used. Aimed to force your hand stay on central keyboard. Also, <left>, <right>, <up>, <down> are unmapeed for the same reason. Please get used to it, to make yourself more efficient.


fast configuration
------------------
fast edit: ,e
fast source .vimrc: auto after save

source code format
------------------
google c++ guideline style used (vim/indent/cpp.vim)
python indent (vim/indent/python.vim)

more
----
there're lots more mapping, please refer to the .vimrc

Install
===========
To activate the configuration files, use
$bash install.sh

insall.sh:
#!/bin/bash
mv ~/.vimrc ~/.vimrc.bak
mv ~/.vim ~/.vim.bak
ln -s `pwd`/vimrc ~/.vimrc 
ln -s `pwd`/vim ~/.vim
